Package: conscia-node
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd, logrotate
Description: Conscia Sovereign Node — Daemon & ConSoul Desktop
 This package provisions a sovereign Exosystem node into the Linux Filesystem
 Hierarchy Standard (FHS). It includes the Conscia P2P daemon (with native
 signaling relay) and the ConSoul desktop administration console.
 .
 The installation is managed via debconf to ensure a standardized,
 interactive configuration experience across all distribution targets.
